reviewText: Almost home movie quality but what can I say...it's Dom! the best parts are of him and his mother walking through the neighborhood and stopping into the different shops. Priceless! the recipes, however are kind of weak, The jokes are corny and old but wait...what can I say.... it's Dom! would have loved more candid footage of him and his mom, maybe some family history, more neighborhood, kind of what Scorsese did, but love what little we got here.
